    <item>
      <title>中国解除对台湾石斑鱼的进口禁令，胡萝卜加大棒外交</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-lifts-ban-taiwanese-grouper-fish-imports-carrot-stick-diplomacy-2023-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国政府宣布，中国将从周五起恢复从台湾进口石斑鱼。一天前，距离台湾大选不到一个月，中国政府终止了对部分化学品进口的关税削减，激怒了台北。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-lifts-ban-taiwanese-grouper-fish-imports-carrot-stick-diplomacy-2023-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 02:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美气候关系为美国大选和特使更换做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-china-climate-relations-brace-us-election-envoy-change-2023-12-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和中国通过首席气候特使的独特关系在气候外交方面取得了巨大胜利，但随着中国特使退休和美国准备大选，两国正在为变革做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-china-climate-relations-brace-us-election-envoy-change-2023-12-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 01:04:14 GMT</pubDate>
